      <t>&lt;p&gt;The purpose of this memo is to document how the requirements for advancing a routing protocol to Draft Standard have been satisfied by Border Gateway Protocol (BGP).  This memo provides information for the Internet community.  It does not specify an Internet standard.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
